.com/news/music/justin-bieber-raps-about-being-high-in-new-video-after-denying-drug-use-3841579">加拿大歌手被认为是关于高高的</a>，引起了公众关注的问题。剪辑是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-biebers-rep-denies-harmful-rumours-of-drug-use-3840651">“逗留”歌手代表关闭在线毒品使用谣言的</a>几天之后，将评论称为“虚假”和“有害”的谣言。</p><p>发言人在与<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/justin-bieber-not-using-drugs-rep-confirm-1235277435/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石乐队</em></a>分享的一份声明中说，公众对艺术家健康的固定是“筋疲力尽和可怜的，表明尽管有明显的事实，但人们仍致力于保持消极，卑鄙，有害的叙述。”</p><p>他们还关闭了猜测，说2024年“对他来说是非常具变革性的，因为他结束了几种不再为他服务的亲密友谊和业务关系。”</p><p>本月初，这位说唱歌手在附近的<a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGwv7zuROJ_/?img_index=6" target="_blank" rel="noopener">烟枪的照片发布了自己的照片</a>后引起了更多关注。 </p><figure id="attachment_3841589" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841589" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841589" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/justin-bieber@2000x1270.jpg" alt="贾斯汀·比伯（Justin Bieber）现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/justin-bieber@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/justin-bieber@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/justin-bieber@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/justin-bieber@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/justin-bieber@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/justin-bieber@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841589" class="wp-caption-text">贾斯汀·比伯（Justin Bieber）现场表演。学分：Joseph Okpako/Wireimage/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>关于比伯（Bieber）的福祉的谣言是在最近几周传播开的狗仔队照片之后，显示了这位歌手看上去很累。鉴于比伯近年来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-able-to-smile-again-following-partial-facial-paralysis-3415171">公开谈论他的健康斗争</a>。这包括在他因“疾病” <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-postpones-north-american-tour-dates-due-to-illness-ive-done-everything-to-get-better-3242083">取消了北美“正义”之旅的开场时间</a>后，在2022年透露了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-reveals-facial-paralysis-from-ramsay-hunt-syndrome-3244867">他在拉姆齐·亨特综合症的诊断</a>。</p><p>除了对他的健康状况的评论外，还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-appears-to-be-back-in-the-studio-3830135">报道说比伯又回到了录音室</a>，并计划很快卷土重来。当新年开始时在工作室里看到他时，这些都得到了加剧，当<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-is-working-on-new-music-with-mk-gee-3790800">MK.Gee透露他一直在与新材料合作时</a>。</p><p>如果工作室的输出作为完整专辑汇集在一起​​，那将是他自2021年“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/justin-bieber-justice-review-2900928">正义</a>”以来的第一个录音室发行。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-bieber-says-he-feels-like-a-fraud-i-have-always-felt-unworthy-3846148">贾斯汀·比伯（Justin Bieber）帖子说，他感觉就像是“欺诈”：“我一直感到不值得”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
